<h5 id="relate-multiple-data-sets">Relate Multiple Data Sets</h5>

<p>If you have two databases that are related, you can connect them using the relation property so you donâ€™t have to manually update each database separately. This feature is particularly useful for linking projects with tasks, clients with projects, or employees with their assignments. This way, you can easily view and manage related information in one place without duplicating data.</p>

