<h5 id="routine-actions-in-one-click">Routine Actions in One Click</h5>

<p>With the button feature, you can automate routine actions, such as creating a new page, inserting blocks, or editing pages, all with a single click. Buttons are highly customizable, allowing you to tailor their functionality to suit specific needs or workflows.</p>

