<h5 id="automate-updates">Automate Updates</h5>

<p>Hereâ€™s another automation trick for databases: Triggers. Triggers reduce the need for manual updates and help keep your data consistent and up to date. For example, if you update an entry, you can set up an automation to automatically notify a group of people, eliminating the need to manually inform them.</p>

